	(1136,146,'main_modules_1_person_1_bio','Steven is Head of Investment Management at Tatton. He has over 10 years of investment industry experience. Prior to joining Tatton he was a member of the investment strategy team responsible for running the £18bn UK Railways Pension Scheme, an economist for the British Government planning future pension provision (NEST) and an investment consultant for a boutique private wealth management firm. He holds a First Class BSc in Economics, an MSc in Economics from The London School of Economics and an MSc in International Securities, Investment &amp; Banking from the ICMA Centre Business School. He is a Chartered Financial Analyst (CFA).'),
