	(2650,259,'main_modules_1_text','<h2>Who are we</h2>\r\nOur solutions are only available through professional advisers. Working closely with advisers ensures that clients’ needs and requirements are constantly taken into account. This gives you complete peace of mind that your investments and future ambitions are in safe hands.\r\n\r\nOur <strong>unique approach</strong> to fund management allows the experienced team to manage your platform based investment portfolio with the timeliness and speed of execution that are usually only available for institutional size clients. We also recognise that our service has to provide good value for money, which is why we believe we are among the most competitive in the marketplace without compromising your clients’ investment objectives.\r\n<h2>We offer peace of mind, ease and efficiency</h2>\r\nTraditional advisory portfolios can often be slow to react to changing market conditions and clunky to administer. Rebalancing is usually performed once a quarter, <strong>only</strong> after seeking permission from you.\r\n\r\nWe take a <strong>different approach</strong>. We can be more agile and nimble when making necessary portfolio changes. Our team can react faster to changing market conditions by selling investments that we think have become expensive and then buy them back again when valuations become more attractive.\r\n\r\nWe aim to give you <strong>peace of mind</strong> by constantly assessing your portfolios to make sure your money is invested in the right place in order to meet your financial objectives.\r\n\r\nWe seek to ensure that your investments always remain suitable for the level of risk you are comfortable with. Tatton do all this for you so that you find managing your money is as easy as possible, allowing you to focus on what is most important to you.'),
