	(2976,301,'main_modules_1_text','<h2>Introducing the\r\nStrategic Managed Portfolio Service (SMPS)</h2>\r\nThe Strategic Managed Portfolio Service is managed by a dedicated team of investment professionals and we use some of the leading names in investment research and fund management to help guide our long-term views.\r\n<h5>Increased flexibility and enhanced returns</h5>\r\nManaging a diversified investment portfolio can be costly and time consuming and investing at just the right time can be more of an art-form than a science.\r\n\r\nWe do all of the hard work for you. We apply a tactical investment overlay on top of the standard advisory models, like those based on OBSR and Vanguard. We gently refine the asset allocation in line with our protective ethos and seek to avoid over-valued assets.\r\n\r\nWe believe this approach can enhance returns. It allows greater flexibility for clients and it improves the responsiveness to changes in markets and lowers the cost. We can pass these cost savings onto you and still offer a fully featured and comprehensive discretionary service.\r\n<h5>A range of six distinct and diversified portfolios</h5>\r\nThe SMPS offers six distinct ranges of portfolios with different management styles and each range consists of six risk-rated diversified portfolios, which invest in a range of underlying investments. This range of investments allows our managers to spread risk across asset classes and ensure that the investment costs are kept as low as possible.\r\n\r\nWe also offer an Ethical portfolio, for those investors seeking to invest in an actively managed and diversified portfolio, based on strict ethical and socially responsible criteria.\r\n\r\nYour financial adviser will help you determine which strategy and portfolio is the most suitable for you, when taking account of your investment objective, time horizon, attitude to and capacity for risk.'),
